  "body": "\r\n***Type***: Bug\r\n\r\n***Summary***: When I update profile data (username/image) for my contact while the device is in airplane mode, - then after I appear online - all contacts who in my 'Contacts list' should see my updated profile. It doesn't happen now, - old profile data is shown for contacts who in my contact list. \r\n\r\n#### Expected behavior\r\nUsername/icon is updated for contacts in my list if I updated profile data while device was offline\r\n\r\n#### Actual behavior\r\nUsername/icon not updated for contacts in my list if I updated profile while device was in offline mode\r\n\r\n### Reproduction\r\n- Open Status on two devices and create Contact1 and Contact2 respectively\r\n- Both contacts add each other 'In Contacts'\r\n- Contact1 enables airplane mode\r\n- Contact1 updates his profile username and image\r\n- Contact1 disables airplane mode\r\n- Contact2 checks whether there is an updated Contact1's profile data on his side \r\n\r\n### Additional Information\r\n* Status version: 0.9.27 Release (it's fine on Release 0.9.26)\r\n* Operating System: Android and iOS\r\n\r\n#### Logs\r\n\r\nTF session for Contact1 for above scenario: https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8579390/sessions/4400475779/?accessToken=VQCmCY5HlSPoeWJN3VTPtXwzd9Y\r\nTF session with logs for Contact2 for above scanario: https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803590-status/builds/8579725/sessions/4400475777/?accessToken=CHQHDUSujjmpnL/vN0I5eqiQYWM\n\n<blockquote><div><strong><a href=\"https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803622-status/builds/8579390/sessions/4400475779/?accessToken=VQCmCY5HlSPoeWJN3VTPtXwzd9Y\">TestFairy: Status 0.9.28 (7620) @2018</a></strong></div></blockquote>\n<blockquote><div><strong><a href=\"https://app.testfairy.com/projects/4803590-status/builds/8579725/sessions/4400475777/?accessToken=CHQHDUSujjmpnL/vN0I5eqiQYWM\">TestFairy: Status 0.9.28 (7620) @2018</a></strong></div></blockquote>",
